  "text": "In vitro Amplification and Sequencing of the Mycobacterial 16S rDNA and hsp65 Genes for NTM Speciation PCR and sequencing of the 577 bp fragment of the mycobacterial 16S rDNA was used for mycobacterial speciation [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Sequencing of the 439 bp hsp65 gene fragment was done for differentiation of some NTM species with similar, or identical 16S rRNA which could not be delineated using the 16S rDNA PCR-sequencing assay [CITATION_3] .",
